- [ ] Based on precise SVG path geometry analysis, not on textual hints.
- [ ] For polygons, count unique vertices, not repeated points on closure.
- [ ] Strict, exhaustive category matching per the Options block.
- [ ] No extra text, explanation, or formatting—just the label.

