       (D) kite — 4 sides, two adjacent pairs of equal length
       (E) line — two points, straight segment
       (F) octagon — 8 sides
       (G) pentagon — 5 sides
       (I) sector — curved portion/arc of a circle
       (J) triangle — 3 sides
       (K) trapezoid — 4 sides, only one pair parallel

5. **Output Rules:**
   - Output ONLY the single letter label for your choice; do not provide any text, explanation, or formatting.
   - Do not repeat or guess a shape name—just supply the correct letter from the options provided.

