  - `L x,y`: Draw a line segment to (x, y).
  - `A rx,ry x-axis-rotation large-arc-flag,sweep-flag x,y`: Draw an arc to (x, y) with the given radii and flags. Used for arcs, circles, ellipses, and sectors.
